碧昂丝的《文艺复兴》电影票房大幅下滑https://www.nme.com/news/film/beyonces-renaissance-movie-suffers-big-drop-at-the-box-office-3556998?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=beyonces-renaissance-movie-suffers-票房大跌Sam WarnerMon, 11 Dec 2023 10:11:23 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3556998 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂斯文艺复兴世界巡回演唱会" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该片在上映第二周末跌至第五位</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/beyonces-renaissance-movie-suffers-big-drop-at-the-box-office-3556998">碧昂丝的《文艺复兴》电影票房大幅下滑</a>后，首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上播出。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂斯文艺复兴世界巡回演唱会" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Beyonce-Renaissance-Tour-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>的《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-renaissance-review-tracklist-artwork-3278806">文艺复兴</a>》演唱会电影上映一周多后，美国票房大幅下滑。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/how-long-will-renaissance-film-beyonce-be-in-cinemas-3550980">《文艺复兴：碧昂丝的电影》将在电影院上映多久？</a></strong></li></ul><p> 《文艺复兴：<em>碧昂斯</em><em>的电影》</em>记录了这位歌手最近的同名巡演，自 12 月 1 日上映以来，首次登上美国国内票房榜首。</p><p>然而，该片在第二个周末的票房收入为 500 万美元（398 万英镑），下降了 77%，目前已跌至第五位，美国总票房为 2800 万美元（2200 万英镑）和 3300 万美元（2600 万英镑）。全球。</p><p>在此之前， <em>《文艺复兴》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/beyonces-renaissance-box-office-falls-short-of-taylor-swifts-eras-tour-movie-3552905">首次冲击了美国票房</a>，首映周末在北美收获了 2100 万美元（1600 万英镑）的票房收入。然而，它仍低于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>最近的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-concert-movie-3513715"><em>Eras Tour</em>电影《Eras Tour》</a> ，后者首周末票房为 9280 万美元（7390 万英镑），全球票房为 2.5 亿美元（1.99 亿英镑）。 </p><p><iframe title="文艺复兴：碧昂丝的电影 |官方预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BGYIXarTNbA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>碧昂丝<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christopher-nolan-calls-taylor-swifts-the-eras-tour-movie-distribution-an-incredible-lesson-for-studios-3518198">与 AMC 影院合作发行这部电影</a>，就像斯威夫特一样，据报道这意味着双方将获得 50% 的票房收入。两人还对彼此的电影表示支持，斯威夫特最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-beyonce-renaissance-film-premiere-3551661">出席了<em>文艺复兴</em>时期在伦敦举行的首映式</a>。</p><p>这部<em>文艺复兴</em>时期的电影现已结束上映，昨天（12 月 10 日）是其最后一次上映。</p><p>本周末，<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/studio-ghibli">吉卜力工作室</a>的新片<em>《男孩与苍鹭》</em>以 1,280 万美元（1,020 万英镑）的成绩夺得美国票房冠军，成为第一部实现这一壮举的原创动画作品。这部电影也是该动画工作室第一部在 IMAX 上上映的电影，这帮助它登上了排行榜的榜首。</p><p>宫崎骏的这部新片将于本月晚些时候在英国上映， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hayao-miyazaki-last-studio-ghibli-film-the-boy-and-the-heron-reviews-3469963">广受好评</a>，并于今年早些时候在本土日本首映，几乎没有进行任何宣传。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christian-bale-florence-pugh-robert-pattinson-english-dub-cast-studio-ghibli-the-boy-and-the-heron-3516883">英语配音演员</a>包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christian-bale">克里斯蒂安·贝尔</a>、弗洛伦斯·皮尤、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-pattinson">罗伯特·帕丁森</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/willem-dafoe">威廉·达福</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-bautista">戴夫·巴蒂斯塔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-hamill">马克</a>·哈米尔、福原凯伦、嘉玛·陈。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/beyonces-renaissance-movie-suffers-big-drop-at-the-box-office-3556998">碧昂丝的《文艺复兴》电影票房大幅下滑</a>后，首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上播出。</p> ;
 《前一天》推出后收到超过 10,000 条负面评论https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-10000-negative-reviews-3557070?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-day-before-10000-negative-reviewsRyan Easby Mon, 11 Dec 2023 10:05:36 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3557070 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="“前一天”信用：Fntastic" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>多人僵尸游戏上周推出</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-10000-negative-reviews-3557070">“The Day Before”一经推出就收到了超过 10,000 条负面评论，</a>最先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="“前一天”信用：Fntastic" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/The-Day-Before-3-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>备受争议的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a>发行<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-day-before">《The Day Before》</a></em>已收到超过 10,000 条谴责游戏质量的负面评论。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/stardew-valley-eric-barone-concernedape-interview-orchestra-tour-haunted-chocolatier-3550713">《星露谷物语》创作者埃里克·巴龙讨论他的音乐生活、巡回演唱会和《闹鬼的巧克力》</a></strong></li></ul><p>经过一系列延迟后， <em>The Day Before</em>于 12 月 7 日推出。在整个预发行期间，该游戏一直被指责为资产翻转，开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fntastic">Fntastic</a>对这些说法提出了异议。</p><p> “请不要指责我们资产翻转；这也不是真的。我们的团队夜以继日地工作了五年，让我们的梦想游戏成为现实。”开发商 <a href="https://twitter.com/FntasticHQ/status/1731680871856369689" target="_blank" rel="noopener">上周在一份声明</a>中表示。</p><p>在同一份声明中，开发商写信给“不相信我们”的人，解释说他们“接受任何形式的批评，并且不会怀恨在心”。</p><p>然而，去年有消息称，Fntastic 使用无偿志愿者来帮助开发游戏，并解释说，全职志愿者基本上被视为有酬工人，而兼职志愿者则获得“酷炫的奖励、参与证书和免费代码”，例如补偿他们在游戏中花费的时间。 </p><figure id="attachment_3391915" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3391915" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3391915" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/The-Day-Before.jpg" alt="“前一天”信用：Fntastic" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/The-Day-Before.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/The-Day-Before-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/The-Day-Before-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/The-Day-Before-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/The-Day-Before-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/The-Day-Before-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3391915" class="wp-caption-text"> “前一天”信用：Fntastic</figcaption></figure><p> Steam 对该游戏的评价目前为“大部分负面”，有超过 10,000 条负面评论抱怨游戏的质量。</p><p> <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/id/poonjabninja/recommended/1372880/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一位评论家写道</a>，开发者“在游戏发布的前一天就开始开发游戏了。事情出来的那天，我们发现自己被骗了。在它发布的第二天，我们发现 Steam 并不关心他们商店里有什么。”</p><p> <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561197963025353/recommended/1372880/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">另一位评论者解释说</a>，他们“对这款游戏所代表的诈骗程度感到震惊。不要购买这款游戏，你会非常失望。”</p><p> “Valve 允许通过他们的平台进行此类行为，这让我更加震惊。”</p><p>其他评论指出，在游戏中执行各种操作时会出现大量崩溃，其中<a href="https://steamcommunity.com/id/UnrealPie/recommended/1372880/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一篇评论指出</a>，当他们开枪时，游戏崩溃了。</p><p>在游戏领域的其他领域，长期陷入困境的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ubisoft">育碧</a>游戏<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/skull-bones">《骷髅与骨头》</a></em>又迎来了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/skull-bones-release-date-the-game-awards-3556255">另一个发行日期</a>。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-10000-negative-reviews-3557070">“The Day Before”一经推出就收到了超过 10,000 条负面评论，</a>最先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
