.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-rm-v-enlistment-111223-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bts">BTS</a>成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rm">RM</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/v">V</a>在今天入伍前给粉丝写了一封信。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/bts-10th-anniversary-retrospective-world-conquering-boyband-evolved-3455187">BTS 10 岁时：征服世界的男孩乐队如何从嘻哈新人演变为不拘一格的偶像</a></strong></li></ul><p>这两名 BTS 成员将于今天（12 月 11 日）入伍，按照韩国男子的要求服义务兵役。这使他们成为乐队中第四和第五位入伍的成员。入伍前夕，BTS 队长 RM 在 Instagram 故事上向粉丝们分享了一封衷心的信。</p><p> “向所有我爱的人问好。那一天终于来了。我觉得我有很多话想对你说，但现在我似乎找不到言语，”他写道，由<a href="https://www.soompi.com/article/1630975wpp/btss-rm-says-goodbye-to-fans-in-heartfelt-letter-ahead-of-military-enlistment" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Soompi</em></a>翻译。</p><p> RM继续说道：“我有信心，并且毫不怀疑，在这一切过去之后，新的美好事物将会在等待着我们。”他补充说，看到他的乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jin">Jin</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-hope">J-hope</a>在各自的军事职业中“英勇地完成如此出色的工作”给了他“无与伦比的勇气”。</p><p> Jin和J-hope是该男子组合中首批入伍的两名成员，前者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jin-bts-enlistment-military-service-3365866">于2022年12月</a>入伍，后者于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-j-hope-farewell-message-military-enlistment-3431852">今年4月</a>入伍。说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/suga">菅义伟</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-suga-enlists-in-the-military-see-you-all-in-2025-3502333">于9月入伍</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3556941" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3556941" style="width: 2500px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3556941" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-rm-enlistment-insta-stories-111223.jpg" alt="bts rm入伍信" width="2500" height="2143" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-rm-enlistment-insta-stories-111223.jpg 2500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-rm-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-400x343.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-rm-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-800x686.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-rm-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-696x597.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-rm-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-1392x1193.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-rm-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-1068x915.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3556941" class="wp-caption-text"> BTS 的 RM 致粉丝的信。致谢：Instagram 上的@rkive。</figcaption></figure><p> RM 表示，他将入伍视为自己和歌迷获得灵感和学习的机会，并且对 18 个月后重返音乐界和歌迷的期待感到欣慰。 “我们以后再见面吧。我很爱你。我希望[这些感受]能够传达给你，哪怕是一点点，”他在结束前写道。</p><p>与此同时，V 还在入伍前一天在 Instagram 上分享了一系列他新发型的照片。 </p><figure id="attachment_3556942" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3556942" style="width: 2500px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3556942" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-v-enlistment-insta-stories-111223.jpg" alt="防弹少年团V入伍" width="2500" height="2143" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-v-enlistment-insta-stories-111223.jpg 2500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-v-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-400x343.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-v-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-800x686.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-v-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-696x597.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-v-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-1392x1193.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/bts-v-enlistment-insta-stories-111223-1068x915.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3556942" class="wp-caption-text"> BTS 12 月 10 日的 V Instagram 故事。来源：Instagram 上的 @thv。</figcaption></figure><p>随后，他在 Instagram 和粉丝社区应用<em>Weverse</em>上上传了自己的相机胶卷，并在后者上给粉丝写了一封信。 “18个月后我会非常健康地回来，所以ARMY，照顾好你的健康，每天寻找幸福，直到我回来，”他写道，由<a href="https://www.koreaboo.com/news/bts-v-posts-message-weverse-along-bunch-photos/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Koreaboo</em></a>翻译。 V在信中还调侃说，他在入伍期间“准备了很多东西”要释放。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0srsu3Pq-i/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 5